videos.headline: UCLA strikes first with 2-yd TD run
videos.description: The Bruins cap off an 80-yard drive with a short goal-line run from RB Bolu Olorunfunmi against the Oklahoma Sooners.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (UCLA strikes first with 2-yd TD run) 2018/09/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sooners answer Bruins with TD
videos.description: Rodney Anderson runs for a 3-yard touchdown to put Oklahoma on the board against UCLA.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Sooners answer Bruins with TD) 2018/09/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray finds Brown for 58-yard catch-and-run TD
videos.description: Kyler Murray hits Marquise Brown for a 58-yard score in the first quarter.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murray finds Brown for 58-yard catch-and-run TD) 2018/09/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Murray scores for the Sooners
videos.description: QB Kyler Murray runs 10 yards to end zone, extending Oklahoma's lead over UCLA 21-7.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Murray scores for the Sooners) 2018/09/08 ESHEET
